        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2435392238" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8938530978772129276">It&apos;s been a while since I read the final, 12th book in the Belgariad by David and Leigh Eddings and it was a little emotional when putting down the book for the last time just now. <br/><br/>I don&apos;t care if the writing is simplified and was probably what would be called Young Adult now, I love these books and am so glad to have revisited them.</span>
  <span id="freeText8938530978772129276" style="display:none">It's been a while since I read the final, 12th book in the Belgariad by David and Leigh Eddings and it was a little emotional when putting down the book for the last time just now. <br /><br />I don't care if the writing is simplified and was probably what would be called Young Adult now, I love these books and am so glad to have revisited them.</span>
